{% extends "layouts/default.twig" %}
{% block content %}
    <div class="container">
        <h2>{{ site.title }} Speaker Information</h2>
        <p>
            We're committed to bringing together some of the most prominent experts from all around the world to share
            their knowledge. We provide travel and accommodation reimbursement to all selected speakers. </p>
        <p>When the Call for Papers closes, the organizers will sort through the submissions, making their selections.
            Speakers will be notified as soon as the selection process is completed.</p>

        <h3>This year's package</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Full conference pass</li>
            <li>
                For speakers remote to the Area:
                <ul>
                    <li>Round-trip airfare/travel reimbursement; we advise speakers to book transport on their own, and
                        then invoice us later
                    </li>
                    <li>3 complimentary hotel nights (extra nights are negotiable and should be announced in advance)
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        If needed we can arrange a pet-friendly accommodation. It needs to be announced in advance
                    </li>
                    <li>Additional complimentary night for Workshop lecturers</li>
                    <li>Pick-up at the Belgrade airport or bus/train station</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>Lunch, receptions and activities included in regular conference</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Equipment and Setup</h3>
        <p>You will be expected to bring your own laptop capable of displaying your presentation and suitable adapters
            for your laptop to connect to a projector. In turn, we will provide:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>A <strong>16:9</strong> aspect ratio screen with <strong>HDMI</strong> cable connections</li>
            <li>An audio system with <strong>wireless microphone</strong></li>
            <li>A podium for presenting from with water provided</li>
        </ul>



        <h3>Session timing</h3>
        <p>All of the <strong>talks are time-limited based</strong> on the conference schedule and the duration of your choice. One talk slot consists of:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your presentation</li>
            <li>Q/A session</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Video recording</h3>
        <p>By submitting your talk (not workshop), you agree that it will be recorded, including you on stage, your
            voice and slides. The video recording will be available free of charge after we publish it on our YouTube
            channel.</p>

        <p>Other important remarks:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Please check if you need a visa for stay in Serbia</li>
            <li>Please bring your own remote control or laser pointer for slides if you need one</li>
            <li>Our staff will take care of time tracking</li>
            <li>Internet access will be provided, but it is strongly suggested that you reduce any dependency on the
                in-house internet connection as much as possible</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Still need help?</h3>
        <p>If you need any additional help or guidance, contact us via email: <a href="mailto:conference@phpsrbija.rs">conference@phpsrbija.rs</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
